---
import Section from "@/layouts/Section.astro";
import Skill from "./Skill.astro";
import Writing from "@/assets/skills/Writing.svg";
import Dev from "@/assets/skills/Dev.svg";
import Detail from "@/assets/skills/Detail.svg";
import Learning from "@/assets/skills/Learning.svg";
import Network from "@/assets/skills/Network.svg";
import Fire from "@/assets/skills/Fire.svg";
import ExternalLink from "@/components/Articles/ExternalLink.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<Section
  class="w-full h-fit flex flex-col 2xl:flex-row content-center flex-nowrap justify-between gap-15 px-5 sm:px-10 md:px-20 py-20"
>
  <div
    class="w-full flex-none text-lg xl:text-xl text-neutral-600 prose prose-h2:text-5xl prose-h2:mb-0 prose-h3:text-5xl shrink-0 prose-h3:mb-13 prose-a:text-sky-600"
  >
    <h2 class="fraunces tracking-tighter">Solutions Engineer</h2>
    <h3 class="fraunces tracking-tighter text-slate-500">Lifelong learner.</h3>

    <p>
      Hey! I'm Alejandro, a <strong>Backend Engineer</strong> with 4 years of experience
      in Golang — my language of choice and the one I follow most closely as it evolves.
    </p>

    <p>
      My journey began with a love for mathematics and a <strong
        >need to understand how things work at their core.</strong
      > That curiosity has led me to tackle ambitious projects from scratch — including
      a fully functional <ExternalLink
        text="Redis clone"
        href="/projects/redis"
      /> and an <ExternalLink text="Interpreter" href="/projects/language" />,
      both built in Go, each with their own dedicated article currently in
      progress.
    </p>

    <p>
      Over the past year I have been freelancing, developing a platform for a
      conglomerate of schools to manage their <strong>notes</strong> and <strong
        >records</strong
      >
      — improving upload times by up to <strong>100x</strong>. You can read more
      about it
      <ExternalLink href="/projects/learning" text="here" />.
    </p>

    <p>
      I also care deeply about <strong>technical communication</strong>. In the
      <ExternalLink href="/projects/redis" text="Redis article" /> I am currently
      writing, I have built <strong>custom animations</strong> explaining algorithms,
      interactive exercises, and step-by-step code walkthroughs to make the internals
      of the system as <strong>accessible as possible</strong>.
    </p>

    <p>
      In my free time I enjoy studying <strong>mathematics</strong> and sharing what
      I am learning with my friends — always with a first principles mindset and
      a drive to build things that actually matter.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-20 w-full flex flex-wrap gap-5 mb-3">
      <Skill skill="Technical Writing">
        <Writing />
      </Skill>
      <Skill skill="First Principles Thinking">
        <Dev />
      </Skill>
      <Skill skill="Attention to Detail">
        <Detail />
      </Skill>
      <Skill skill="Self Directed Learning">
        <Learning />
      </Skill>
      <Skill skill="Problem Decomposition">
        <Network />
      </Skill>
      <Skill skill="Lots of Passion">
        <Fire />
      </Skill>
    </section>
  </div>

  <Image
    class="object-cover object-top h-full min-h-100 w-full aspect-video 2xl:w-2/5 rounded-3xl border-4 border-white shadow-md shadow-black/80"
    src="/images/me.webp"
    alt="me"
    width={450}
    height={500}
  />
</Section>
